{"tid":2100524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應Kanye West參選總統一事 川普：非常有趣","createTime":"2020-07-09T06:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T06:15:56.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c186685ce472009dda49e2c21610e5e5e7baeb6","tid":2100524,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"現年43歲的「肯爺」肯伊威斯特過去一直是川普的支持者，卻於美國國慶日當天在推特（Twitter）發文寫道：「透過相信上帝、凝聚願景、建設未來，我們如今將體現美國希望，我要競選美國總統。」<br />\n<br />\n文末還附上美國國旗圖案及「2020願景」的主題標籤。這則推文至今已獲得逾50萬次轉推、超過一百萬次按讚。<br />\n<br />\n對於肯伊威斯特有意參選，川普昨天在白宮回覆記者提問時表示：「非常有趣。」<br />\n<br />\n但川普指出，有些州的登記參選時間已經截止，而且肯伊威斯特缺乏選戰所需的基礎組織架構。<br />\n<br />\n不過，肯伊威斯特顯然信心滿滿，他接受富比世雜誌（Forbes）訪問時表示，參選就是為了要勝選。<br />\n<br />\n肯伊威斯特在今天出刊的訪問中說：「在這場訪問，我要脫下紅色帽子。」他指的是川普著名的「讓美國再次偉大」（Make America Great Again）紅色棒球帽。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007080297.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202007080297.aspx&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=c783eed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007080297.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"06f46ba219a825f2e629d74162b8e411011abe9d","tid":2100524,"uid":326881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">借位，兩分鐘行動POST</span><br />\n<br />\n舉報港奸，人人有責 [實用舉報文英文範本]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2100460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2100460</a>"},{"pid":"32269a2071e82b5a5e791153556c7ec005f4aee9","tid":2100524,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"fish dick"},{"pid":"7d2f22eca336df9fba6e63a9ef834622a7b94c1d","tid":2100524,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"講下者<br />\n選一次要起碼幾千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}